@startuml SC-31-Messagerie
!theme plain
title Diagramme de Collaboration - Messagerie Client (Consultant)

object Consultant
object "Interface Messagerie" as InterfaceMsg
object "Service Messages" as ServiceMsg
object "Base Données" as BaseDonnees
object "Service Notification" as ServiceNotification
object "Service Audit" as ServiceAudit
object Client

Consultant --> InterfaceMsg : 1: acceder("Messages")
InterfaceMsg --> ServiceMsg : 2: obtenirMessages(consultantId)
ServiceMsg --> BaseDonnees : 3: executerRequete(messages)
BaseDonnees --> ServiceMsg : 3.1: listeMessages[]
ServiceMsg --> InterfaceMsg : 4: afficher(conversations)
InterfaceMsg --> Consultant : 4.1: montrer(liste)

Client --> InterfaceMsg : 5: envoyer(message)
InterfaceMsg --> ServiceMsg : 6: envoyerMessage({clientId, contenu})
ServiceMsg --> BaseDonnees : 7: sauvegarderMessage(message)
BaseDonnees --> ServiceMsg : 7.1: messageId

ServiceMsg --> ServiceAudit : 7.2: enregistrerAction("MESSAGE_ENVOYE")
ServiceAudit --> BaseDonnees : 7.3: sauvegarderLog()

ServiceMsg --> ServiceNotification : 8: notifierConsultant(messageId)
ServiceMsg --> InterfaceMsg : 9: succes()
InterfaceMsg --> Client : 10: afficher("Message envoye")

Consultant --> InterfaceMsg : 11: consulter(conversation)
InterfaceMsg --> ServiceMsg : 12: obtenirConversation(clientId)
ServiceMsg --> BaseDonnees : 13: executerRequete(fil)
BaseDonnees --> ServiceMsg : 13.1: messages[]
ServiceMsg --> InterfaceMsg : 14: afficher(discussion)
InterfaceMsg --> Consultant : 15: montrer(conversation)

Consultant --> InterfaceMsg : 16: repondre(message)
InterfaceMsg --> ServiceMsg : 17: envoyerReponse({conversationId, contenu})
ServiceMsg --> BaseDonnees : 18: sauvegarderMessage(reponse)
BaseDonnees --> ServiceMsg : 18.1: messageId

ServiceMsg --> ServiceAudit : 18.2: enregistrerAction("REPONSE_ENVOYEE")
ServiceAudit --> BaseDonnees : 18.3: sauvegarderLog()

ServiceMsg --> ServiceNotification : 19: notifierClient(messageId)
ServiceMsg --> InterfaceMsg : 20: succes()
InterfaceMsg --> Consultant : 21: afficher("Reponse envoyee")

note right of ServiceMsg
Messagerie Directe (SC-31):
- Communication directe/informelle
- Conversations par fil
- Sans ticket formel
- Notifications en temps reel
- Voir SC-12 pour support tickets
end note

@enduml
